name: Cyborg Warrior - Bionic Conflict Destroys Humanity
description: A 2015 soundtrack album from the comic book of the same title. Consists of six retrosynth genre tracks. With the title in Indonesian. The comic itself tells about the life of an unemployed cyborg who is assigned to protect his village from the invasion of evil cyborg troops. Set in Indonesia in 1989. This is a story about Indonesian cyberpunk or can be referred to as "cyberempunk".
